affix.word_mean: adj. & adv. 处于睡眠状态的

word_mean_info__list.difference: 作表语，多用于非正式的英语里，指处于睡着的状态，侧重动作的结果。
最常用词，指人昏昏欲睡，或沉睡时的寂静状态。

word_group.brief_definition: 不专心的；不留神的；不活跃的
半睡着了；半睡；半睡半醒

bilingual.source: The baby is asleep in the crib.
I found him asleep on the couch.
bilingual.target: 我发现他在沙发上睡着的。

bilingual.source: The dog is asleep by the fireplace.
What time did you fall asleep last night?
He was so tired that he was asleep within minutes.
bilingual.target: 他太累了，几分钟内就睡着的。

bilingual.source: But when we were asleep we had to contain them in a large room.
bilingual.target: 但当我们睡着的时候，我们必须把它们关在一个大房间里。

bilingual.source: Physical problems are another factor that can cause students to fall asleep in class.
bilingual.target: 身体问题是导致学生在课堂上睡着的另一个因素。
睡着的这个婴儿还在睡觉吗？
当我睡着的时候也是死的

yingyinNormal.en: We could wait 'til he's asleep and kill him dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们可以等到他睡着的时候然后把他杀了。

yingyinNormal.en: He said he'd bring me a present. You're not supposed to be listening to that. You're supposed to be asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说要给我带礼物。你不应该听到那些的，你应该睡着的。

yingyinNormal.en: George is asleep. Peppa is asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小猪乔治睡着了。佩奇睡着了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George are asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩佩和乔治睡着了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa, George. Mummy is asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇，乔治！嘘，妈妈已经睡着了！

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard's asleep. Thanks for the update.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱纳德睡着了。谢谢你的最新更新。

yingyinNormal.en: No matter what I did, I couldn't fall asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论我怎么试，就是睡不着。

yingyinNormal.en: He looks a lot better. No, he's still asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他看上去好多了，不，他还在睡呢。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll see you when I get home? If I'm asleep...
yingyinNormal.zh: 回家见？如果我睡了……

yingyinNormal.en: The Tooth Fairy has arrived. But Peppa is asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这时牙仙子来了，但是佩琪睡着了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello. Where are Peppa and George? They are asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们好啊！你们好！佩奇和乔治在哪里啊？他们都睡了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George are in their little beds, fast asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和乔治躺在床上睡着了。

yingyinNormal.en: Granny Pig? Peppa? George? You should be in bed asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 奶奶？佩琪？乔治？你们两个不是应该睡着了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George are fast asleep in their holiday house.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和乔治在他们假期的房子里很快就睡着了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George are fast asleep in their holiday house.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和乔治在他们度假的房子里很快就睡着了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George are fast asleep in their holiday house.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和乔治在他们假期的房子里很快就睡着了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa, George, wake up. It's morning. What? I wasn't asleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩琪，乔治，起床了，已经早上了。什么，我没有睡着。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, and then I was, like, "If I fall asleep now, I'll get six hours' sleep. But if I fall asleep now, I'll get five hours' sleep."
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道的，我会想如果现在睡着，我顶多睡六小时，但是如果我现在睡着，我顶多睡五个小时。

yingyinNormal.en: You fell asleep, didn't you? Well, maybe I fell asleep just for a little bit. Next time, I will stay awake, and I will see the Tooth Fairy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩琪，你睡着了是不是？那个 我想我可能真的睡着了一会吧，但是下一次我一定会醒着等她来的，我一定要见见牙仙子。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, she's asleep now. Stop forcing that thing on her. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，她现在在睡觉呢。别再塞这玩意儿给她。好的。
